Under Armour’s mission is simple: to make you better.

UA Tech is our original go-to training gear: loose, light, and it keeps you cool. That means this long sleeve training shirt does everything you need it to. UA Tech fabric is quick-drying, ultra-soft & has a more natural feel. Material wicks sweat & dries really fast. New, streamlined fit & shaped hem. Loose: Fuller cut for complete comfort. 100% Polyester.
